309
00:18:23,670 --> 00:18:25,070
Looking forward to working with you.

310
00:19:02,630 --> 00:19:03,700
Next

311
00:19:19,400 --> 00:19:20,070
Next

312
00:19:23,100 --> 00:19:23,430
Agh!

313
00:19:25,300 --> 00:19:27,700
